                "url": "/topics/some"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bill_medley_784980",
        "quote": "Elvis was a great guy. We'd just horse around together or go to see a movie. He drove me around Graceland in a golf cart. He was a fan of our music and was curious about how I sounded so black.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bill Medley",
            "url": "/quotes/bill_medley_784980"
