    {
        "url": "/quotes/bill_medley_784952",
        "quote": "I had fans, and the industry and everybody saying, 'Keep the Righteous Brothers going; keep the music alive,' and I really didn't want to do that. I had sung with a couple of guys who would supposedly be really good Bobby Hatfields, and I thought, 'Oh geez, it's really anti-climatic.'",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bill Medley",
            "url": "/quotes/bill_medley_784952"
