    {
        "url": "/quotes/bill_medley_784960",
        "quote": "Opening for The Beatles in San Francisco at the Cow Palace was great. It was terrific fun to do. The tour itself, I must say, wasn't a whole lot of fun, artistically. It was just more kind of interesting.",
